(6, 0, 'Conference', 'Great minds create great future. Join them!', 'conference-events', '<p>Learn, absorb and apply knowledge gained by experts of your field at these conferences. Choose from these top conferences, seminars, workshops and meet-ups. Register Now</p>', '1537689834.png', '1537691889.png', '1540827660.jpg', '1537689799.png', '1545503281.jpg', '1535114351.jpg', 6, 'upcoming conferences, conference alert, conference in India, international conference, conference meeting lists, seminars and conference', 'Learn, absorb and apply knowledge gained by experts of your field at these national and international conferences in India. Choose from these top conferences alerts, seminars, workshops and meet-ups.', '29 Upcoming Conferences Event List | International Meetups Events in India', 1, 1, '2018-08-24 07:09:11', '2019-01-21 19:58:27'),
