 style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">They also offer following optional services on request and will be charged accordingly:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Transportation from Delhi/Chandigarh to Shimla.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Paragliding</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Skiing</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Barbeque</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Corporate Setup</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day tour of Shimla, Kufri &amp; Fagu</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Premium Alcohol</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One bottle of mineral water per person per day</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Bonfire on party day</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The camping location is picture perfect destination away from all the hustle and bustle of the city. The beauty of the camp will be enhanced by the meandering of the river Sutlej and nearby mountaintop. The scenic trails are perfect for leisurely strolls amidst the Pines and Deodars under the snow-capped mountains. Doesn&rsquo;t this description soothe your minds already? Imagine what it would be like to actually witness it! </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Don&rsquo;t give this breathtaking view a miss for the world. Hurry and pack your bags to embark on this trip to Naldehra hills. To buy tickets click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; Button.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">They&#39;ve curated three packages especially suitable for you. Select from the below&nbsp;</span>get going on the best&nbsp;<strong>New Year&rsquo;s Eve party ever</strong>!</span></p>', '2018-12-30', '2019-01-01', '08:00:00', '23:50:00', '1542563699.jpg', '1542335443.jpg', 16, '', 'https://www.triphermit.com/new-year-event', 'https://www.triphermit.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/triphermitexpeditions/', 'https://twitter.com/triphermitexp', '', '', 'https://plus.google.com/117941978820901420773', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfJ1h_4dwkeiFiFCII2z14Q', '', 0, 245, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-16 09:30:43', '2018-12-06 00:35:07'),
(30, 'Grandest New Year Celebration (HANGOVER - 2019)', 'grandest-new-year-celebration-hangover-2019', 5, 0, '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">Come and celebrate this grand New Year Party with your family &amp; loved </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">one&#39;s</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\"> at Bravura Gold</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">....</span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">New year holds a different meaning for everyone. For some</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> it means 365 new days and 365 new chances. While for some, it means new resolutions and promises. The clock is ticking much faster now and the New Year is just around the corner. Another great year is coming to an end. All of us have started planning how to end 2018 in a fun way and on a great note. The celebrations have to be in order now. Get ready for the most sensational way of counting down the last hours of 2018! <strong>Meerut&#39;s Biggest &amp; Craziest New Year celebration is back with &ldquo;Grandest Night Club&rdquo; theme set-up ever seen in Meerut &amp; NCR</strong>. A family event by <strong>Bravura Gold Resort </strong>that is highly secure awaits you all. Bravura Gold Resort has a track record of hosting the most successful New Year events in Meerut.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">Stop all the thinking!!! Come and celebrate this grand New Year Party with your family &amp; 