(33, 'Essel World Bignite 2018: India’s Largest Open Air Party', 'essel-world-bignite-2018', 5, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Essel World </span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Bignite</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\"> is back with India&rsquo;s largest open-air party! The most happening New Year Eve</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">....</span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">While some New year parties make people nostalgic of the time that has fled by, most </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">mean</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> new beginnings, new opportunities </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and,</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> new hopes. People meet and greet each other, eat and dance together and reminisce the good and bad times they have seen in the past year. And </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">furthermore</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">, they look forward to celebrating the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> year in style! </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Essel World Bignite is back with </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">India&rsquo;s</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> largest </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">open-air</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> party! The most happening New Year Eve Party in town! And trust us, it only gets bigger and better as years pass by. This 31st December, party till the wee hours along with incredible music and dance, thrilling rides, delectable food and drinks, international acts and a carnival where the fun doesn&rsquo;t stop till the sun comes up on a brand new year!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\">Enjoy unlimited rides and slides right from 8 pm onwards. So enter 2019 with a non-stop party! Put on your party hats, dancing shoes and safety belts. Enjoy like no one is watching!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\">New year party with endless fun, thrill, non-stop music, food, and</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> drinks.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">HIGHLIGHTS:</span></span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">64 acres of space with more than 70+ Rides &amp; Attractions for all age groups</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Electrifying lights with thunderous sound across 4 dance floors</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Welcome 2018 Carnival with International Acts</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Welcome Band</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">MAGICAL Parade</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-famil