(34, 'Desert New Year Festival in Jaisalmer, 2019 -  3D/2N', 'new-year-festival-jaisalmer', 4, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">What makes a dull and boring new year fun and special? Camels, long stretches of sands.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">What makes a dull and boring new year fun and special? Camels, long stretches of sands, glorious sunrise. Have you been able to make a guess yet? We are talking about New year celebration at Thar Desert people! Come and witness a once in a lifetime experience in the chilling deserts of Thar. Make it a memory to be cherished for a lifetime. &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#333333\"><strong>Now, it&rsquo;s your turn to explore yourself into the exciting extravaganza, which continues for about three days in the middle of historical forts, ancient haveli, Jain temples, majestic palaces, and indigenous culture as well.</strong> </span>Romantic, remote and unspoiled, the location comes to life during the extravaganza of the delights of the desert. The immense desert offers more than one can expect, so enjoy the privilege of laying in the sand with bright illuminating stars overhead and the desert silence ready to engulf you. Catch a glimpse of the local culture, tradition with the folk songs and dances to amuse and entertain you.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Date</u></strong>:<strong> </strong>29th December 2018 to 2nd January 2019</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Pickup</u></strong>: Dhola Kuan Metro Station / Iffco Chowk, Gurgaon at 8.00 pm on 29th December 2018.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Itinerary </u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>29th Dec 2018 (Day 1)</strong></em>: Departure From Delhi - Depart from Delhi for Jaisalmer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>30th Dec 2018 (Day 2)</strong></em>: Jaisalmer Sightseeing- Arrival Jaisalmer in the afternoon and check in at the hotel. After&nbsp;resting, head towards Jaisalmer for local sightseeing which includes:</span></span>\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Jaisalmer Fort,</span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Nathmal Ji Ki Haveli,</span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Patwaon Ki Haveli,</span></span></li>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Gadisar Lake.</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Overnight Stay at the hotel.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>31st Dec 2018 (Day 3)</strong></em>: New Year&#39;s Eve Party &amp; Camping - On reaching the campsite en route Bada Bagh and Kuldhara, break for tea &amp; snacks followed by Desert Camel Safari and later Desert Jeep Safari.</span></span>\r\n\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;Inclusions:</span></span>\r\n\r\n		<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Live Rajasthani Kalbeliya Dance Performance.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;Live Rajasthani Folk Singers.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Live Performances by Artists.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">DJ Party and Bollywood Dance.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Fire &amp; Cracker Show.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Variety of Rajasthani Dishes For Dinner.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Desert Camel Safari.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Desert Jeep Safari.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Free Alcohol.</span></span></li>\r\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Overnight stay at luxury swiss camps.</span></span></li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><strong>1 Jan 2019 (Day 4)</strong></em>: Departure - Breakfast followed by departure for the destination.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif