(39, 'New Year Eve Under the Stars - White Nights, Karjat', 'new-year-eve-moonstone-hammock', 4, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Experience New Year Eve at White Nights, which is going to happen from 30 December 2018 to 1 January.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Any plans for the upcoming New Year&rsquo;s Eve? Don&rsquo;t say that you are going to drink and dance till you drop at any nearby bar or lounge which you have visited so many times before! Try something new and exciting this New Year&rsquo;s Eve. <strong>Experience New Year Eve at White Nights, which is going to happen from 30 December 2018 to 1 January 2019 at Moonstone Hammock Camping Ground, Karjat.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Book your tickets</strong> for this two nights and three days event, and bring in the New Year under the stars. This event promises an immersive camping experience with live music, good food, and festivities. Also, don&rsquo;t be surprised if you find some new friends here! It&rsquo;s the magic of this place that people from different walks of life come together and enjoy wonderful activities together. Along with </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">live</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> band music, you can also enjoy movie screening, barbecue, and many adventure activities.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"color:black\">Itinerary</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Day 1 (30th December)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get ready for the good old kayaking, if you are up for some adventure! The best way to start interacting with your fellow campers is to indulge in a friendly competition with them. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Gather for some delicious barbecue by the bonfire.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">If you are a movie buff, come to the theatre, which has been created beautifully between rumbling leaves and relaxing wind. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Day 2 (31st December)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Enhance your kayaking skills with another adventure session.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Unwind yourself over board games at the </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Hippie</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> Cafe.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get your shades and costumes and enter the Sundowner Pool Party in style. Enjoy there with your favorite tunes being played in the background. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Deck up for the New Year Party, with two live bands geared up to make every moment memorable.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Gather by the bonfire to satiate your taste buds with some ravishing dishes. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Day 3 (1st January)</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Welcome 2019 with sumptuous breakfast</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Check-out from the campsite by 11:30 am</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Walk into the New Year with an awesome mood and in the company of some amazing people, some of them might turn out to be your new friends!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em>Book your tickets now as it&rsquo;s a limited period offer!&nbsp;</em></span><em>For best price &amp; booking click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; button. </em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ground Tent:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">1 Night Camp &ndash; INR 4990</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">2 Night Camp &ndash; INR 8500</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Floating Tent:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">1 Night Camp &ndash; INR 5990</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">2 Night Camp &ndash; INR 9500</span></span></p>', '2018-12-30', '2019-01-01', '15:00:00', '11:30:00', '1543036937.jpg', '1543036936.jpg', 26, '', 'https://www.goeventz.com/event/new-year-eve-moonstone-hammock/81964', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/moonstonehammockofficial/', 'https://twitter.com/MoonstoneHam', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/moonstonehammockofficial/?hl=en', '', '', '', 0, 633, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-24 12:22:17', '2018-12-06 00:32:04'),
(40, 'Delhi Food Truck Festival 2019: New Delhi', 'delhi-food-truck-festival-2019', 3, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This is the best time for foodies to indulge in their love for warm, mouth-watering dishes under the.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you up for a foody affair? Oh Yeah! How can anyone say no to a lovely winter meal? This is the best time for foodies to indulge in their love for warm, mouth-watering dishes under the stars. The <strong>Delhi Food Truck Festival </strong>is back, and this time with even more options. You can&rsquo;t just stop drooling when your favourite <strong><em>dahi bhallas</em></strong> and <strong><em>papri chats</em></strong> are there along with the waffles, everything available in one place. It&rsquo;s truly a fun time for Delhiites over food. The food truck festival promises some truly good times.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Don&rsquo;t resist yourself from digging into mouth-watering delicacies, as food trucks from all corners of the city are ready to halt again at the <strong>Jawahar Lal Nehru Stadium from 14 to 16 December 2018. </strong>Not just food, this festival is also about good music, live bands, and celebrities. It&rsquo;s the complete food, fun, and fiesta for<strong> </strong><em><strong>Delhi wallas and wallis.</strong> </em>You can also bring your kids along, as there are amazing gaming zones for them to go on a gaming frenzy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em>Food &amp; Fun together at the Festival!</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What are the highlights of this year&rsquo;s Delhi Food Truck Festival?</strong> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Well, don&rsquo;t forget to visit Delhi 6 Lane, DFTF Hatt and Flavours of India at the festival! And while your favourite dishes are being prepared, you can sneak into the Gaming/ Experience zone to try your hand at your </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">favourite</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> outdoor activities. Live stage performances will further add some pinch of warmth to chilly winter evenings.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What you must do at the festival</strong>?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Enjoy the snow dance. Yes, you heard it right! Pull over a bomber jacket and layer up, as the snow dance will dip the temperature significantly.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Hurry. Get your passes for the festival today!&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>One Day Pass</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Early Bird Ticket: INR 99</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Season Pass</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Early Bird Ticket: INR 249</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Make a Note:</strong></u><br />\r\nEntry is from gate number 14, so park your car accordingly (if you&#39;re traveling by one). For booking click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; button.</span></p>', '2018-12-14', '2018-12-16', '10:00:00', '23:00:00', '1543311069.jpg', '1543311069.jpg', 28, '', 'https://insider.in/delhi-food-truck-festival-december14-2018/event', 'http://delhifoodtruckfestival.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/DelhiFoodTruckFestival/', 'https://twitter.com/DFTF_IN', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/delhifoodtruckfestival/', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGf9LOZS4g9uOxptqaVvXog?view_as=subscriber&app=desktop', '', 0, 1529, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-27 16:31:09', '2018-11-27 16:53:20'),
(41, 'STARup Summit 2019: The Ultimate Networking Experience', 'starup-summit-2019', 6, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">STARup is an ultimate networking experience for investors, entrepreneurs, government officials, corporate....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>STARup</strong> is an ultimate networking experience for investors, entrepreneurs, government officials, corporate representatives, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> influencers. Business personalities from the Indian, Asian and European start-up ecosystems come together to participate in workshops, joint panels, </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">roundtable</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> sessions </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> one-on-one meetings. It&rsquo;s the ideal business atmosphere for start-ups, with active investors and experienced entrepreneurs under one roof to make the event productive for everyone.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">First launched in 2016, STARup was successful in bringing more than 1500 participants together during the last event to create a worthwhile start-up community. This year, it&rsquo;s going to be even bigger and better with renowned speakers like <strong>Sunita G.R. (Head of Marketing Facebook)</strong>, <strong>Anubhav Modi (Associate Director Finance, Bira91)</strong> and many more coming to the event. Some of the best-known investors will also be there on the pitch jury and reverse investor pitches to help start-ups get the right boost. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">There will be different tracks at the event &ndash; The Stage, The Fireside, Inception, Spotlight, 1-on-1 Track. During the 1-on-1 track, start-up attendees with </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>gold</strong> pass will get time for 30-minutes, intense meeting with investors to pitch their idea. </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">So, bring your best game </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">at</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> this track and you may get the much-deserved chance to take your start-up to the next level. While at <em>The Stage</em>, ten handpicked start-ups will get a chance to pitch their idea in front of the investor pool. If your start-up deals in any pathbreaking product, you can use the <em>Spotlight</em> track to launch your offerings and let the world know about it in one shot. The format of <em>Fireside</em> includes activities like vertical focused discussions, masterclasses, Ask Me Anything sessions and Fireside chats. And then, you have <em>Inception</em>, which will allow young guns, achievers </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> maestros to share their perspective and get a glimpse of what the future has to offer.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Book your Gold Passes today</strong> to be a part of the <strong>1-on-1 track</strong> and many more exciting sessions at the event.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">What are you waiting for? For Registration &amp; more details - &nbsp;click on &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; Button. <strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Start-up Delegate: INR 2000</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Corporate Delegate: INR 4000</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Student: INR 500</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Visitor (Grab the Gold): INR 750</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<strong>Gold Package Includes: </strong>INR 8000</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All included in access package</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">1-on-1 meeting with 3 investors</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '2019-01-18', '2019-01-19', '09:30:00', '17:30:00', '1543406570.jpg', '1543406570.jpg', 29, '', 'http://www.starup.in/#register', 'http://www.starup.in/', 'https://www.facebook.com/STARupSummit/', 'https://twitter.com/STARupSummit', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/starupsummit', '', '', '', 'Speakers', 0, 146, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-28 19:02:50', '2018-11-28 23:48:02'),
(42, 'Pet Fed: India\'s Biggest Pet Festival - Delhi | Mumbai | Bangalore', 'pet-festival-india', 10, 0, '<p>India&#39;s Biggest Pet Festival&nbsp;is back in Delhi, Mumbai &amp; Bengaluru to give all the pet lovers...</p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One of your favourite weekends of 2018 is just a few days away. <strong>Pet Fed</strong> is an ideal place for pet lovers of the town. Your furry friends are waiting for you, and are ready to give you a warm welcome. Join in with or without your pet friend and enjoy great time with those who are craving for your love and attention.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">At the event, there will be many exciting activities like games and rides. Those who are looking for some fun time with pet animals can come at off-leash zones and indulge in a wonderful experience. In this area, you can find <strong>doggy ball pools</strong>, <strong>trampolines</strong>, <strong>tunnels</strong>, <strong>hurdles</strong>, <strong>Have-A-Go Agility</strong> and<strong> various fun games</strong>. Don&rsquo;t forget to take your pet to the Temptation Alley, where your dog will be tempted by treats like food and toys while you are trying to call him/ her back to you. If your pet succeeds in resisting the temptation, he/ she will win the round and get an exciting gift hamper!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other exciting activities are lined up at the <strong>Pet Fed 2018</strong>, <strong>such as fashion show for pets with Dino Morea and security dog show.</strong> There is also a dedicated cat zone for your feline friend, where she can enjoy exclusive games. And, there will be the aqua world, which will take you to the ecosphere that bleeds blue.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">There will be more than <strong>100 stalls</strong> for your pet at the event. So, get ready to enjoy a memorable stroll with your pet all across the event location. The more you explore the place, the higher are your chances of discovering something awesome. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">We know, the more is merrier! If you want to bring a new furry into your family, adoption camps are just for you. There you can discover dogs of over <strong>50 breeds </strong>(including our desi ones). Don&rsquo;t forget to be there at the time of <strong>Pet Fed Awards</strong>, which aim to honour some amazing work in the pet care industry. You can also vote online in categories like <strong>Best Debut Award- 2018</strong>, <strong>Doggie Baker &amp; Chef Award - 2018, Glamorous Groomer Award- 2018</strong> and <strong>Veterinarian Award- 2018</strong>. Remember, every vote count!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Book online to get amazing discounts! -&nbsp;Click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; button.</span></p>', '2019-01-19', '2019-01-20', '11:00:00', '21:00:00', '1543428592.jpg', '1543428592.jpg', 30, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/pet-fed-mumbai-2019?acode=aAcuPF', 'http://petfed.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/petfedindia/', 'https://twitter.com/petfedindia', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/petfedindia/', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXCUKRYHbplagxYM_MTukag', '', 0, 605, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-29 01:09:52', '2018-12-29 17:40:29'),
(43, 'UltraViolet Music Festival - New Year Eve 2018', 'ultraviolet-music-festival-new-year-eve-2018', 1, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The fifth edition of UltraViolet Music Festival is finally happening! People of Ahmedabad need to get ....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The fifth edition of <strong>UltraViolet Music Festival</strong> is finally happening! People of Ahmedabad need to get ready to groove. Mesmerizing feats of Bollywood and international acts and a lot more are going to happen under the starts in Ahmedabad for the first time. So, <strong>block your dates for the New Year Eve as it&rsquo;s going to be bigger and better this time. </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Along with mesmerizing Bollywood and international feats, there will be some live fire acts, LED Tron artists and belly dance performances. Aren&rsquo;t you excited to see world-class fire jugglers and LED dancers in action! </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This one of the most talked-about music festivals in the town, and is the ideal New Year Eve&rsquo;s destination for people of all age groups. Come with your family and friends to ring in the New Year with renowned artists performing to some enthralling instrumental music scores. Many more artists are lined up for the festival. Stay tuned for more updates. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">DJs for the festival are practicing hard to create a blend of all genres of music and catch the interest of attendees with varied tastes and preferences. And, there will be a variety of sumptuous delicacies to satiate their taste buds. Any celebration is incomplete without food, and this festival has it all that you expect on a day of celebration. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get ready for the most exciting audio-visual experience ever.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Ticket Details </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Stag Pass &ndash; INR 600 per Person (General Conclave), Qty to be sold 500</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">VIP Pass &ndash; INR 1000 per Person, Qty to be Sold 200</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Group Pass &ndash; INR 2500 (5 People per Group Pass), General Conclave, Qty to be Sold 300</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">VVIP Tables &ndash; INR 10000 per Table (5 people Per table), Food inclusive, Qty to be sold 15 tables</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Time of Event </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Start time: 31st Dec, 2018 6:30 PM </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">End time: 1st Jan, 2019, 00:15 AM</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Book your early bird tickets today! - </strong>Click on &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; Button</span></span></p>', '2018-12-31', '2019-01-01', '18:30:00', '00:15:00', '1543466553.jpg', '1543466553.jpg', 31, '', 'https://allevents.in/ahmedabad/ultraviolet-music-festival-new-year-eve-2018/80002022928333', 'https://www.shamrockmedeve.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/shamrockmedeve', 'https://twitter.com/EventsShamrock', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shamrockevents/', 'https://www.instagram.com/shamrock_events/', 'https://plus.google.com/u/1/115612859799825895789', '', '', 0, 167, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-11-29 11:42:33', '2018-11-29 11:59:19'),
