(45, 'Sunburn Festival 2018: The Carnival of Dance & Music', 'sunburn-festival-2018', 1, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After 11 years of outstanding dance and music display, the Sunburn Festival is set to kick off...</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After 11 years of outstanding dance and music display, the <strong>Sunburn Festival </strong>is set to kick off with its season 12. This year, <strong>Sunburn Festival 2018</strong> will be taking place in<strong> Pune</strong> at &lsquo;<strong>Oxford Gold Resorts</strong>&rsquo;. It promises to be even bigger and better with more reasons for dance &amp; music enthusiast to create memories that last forever. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Over the years, new technologies and stage designs have given the Sunburn Festival a more contemporary look that catches the fancy of today&rsquo;s youth. With unique and creative themes every year, Sunburn Festival is truly redefining the way people enjoy music in this country. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This year, you have a grand festival arena and a huge artistic line up to enhance your experience. To ensure hassle-free entertainment for the visitors, Festival organizers have pulled up their socks. From parking facilities to health and safety amenities, everything will be taken care of quite well. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Highlights of The Festival</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Axwell &amp; </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Ingresso</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">: The famous Swedish DJ duo will be performing at the Sunburn Festival on 29 December 2018. They made their debut performance in Governors Ball Music Festival in New York City in 2014, and there is no looking back. Aren&rsquo;t you excited to witness them performing on their popular electronic music?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Armin Van Buuren</strong>: The famous Dutch DJ, record producer and remixer from South Holland </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">is</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> ready to make people go crazy with his trance music on December 31, 2018.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Alan Walker</strong>: This Norwegian DJ and record producer is all set to pull in the crowd with his &lsquo;Faded&rsquo;, which has already received Platinum certification in more than 10 countries. He will also be performing on December 30, 2018.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>DJ Snake</strong>: And your favorite DJ Snake will be performing on 31 December 2018 to captivate you with his chartbusters like Da Vinci and Out with The Wild.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Along with them, many other artists from the world of dance and music are lined up for the Festival, such as Nucleya, Mercer, Vini Vici, Salvatore Ganacci and more.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Entry Ticket</strong>: 1799/ - Onwards</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can book camping and concert tickets separately or in a single transaction. For Book, your tickets online <strong>-</strong>&nbsp;Click on <strong>&quot;Official Ticket URL&quot;</strong>. This 3-days festival is undoubtedly an experience to be a part of.</span></span></p>', '2018-12-29', '2018-12-31', '18:00:00', '01:00:00', '1543639446.jpg', '1543639446.jpg', 1, '', 'https://sunburn.in/festival-2018/', 'https://sunburn.in/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sunburnfestival', 'https://twitter.com/sunburnfestival', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/sunburnfestival/', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/sunburnfestival', '', 0, 509, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-01 11:44:06', '2018-12-01 11:47:13'),
(46, 'Sparkling Forest New Year Bash 2019 - Navi Mumbai', 'sparkling-forest-new-year-bash-2019-mumbai', 5, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">With tick-tack of the clock and the approaching end of the year, mark this end and a fresh start of the....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">With tick-tack of the clock and the approaching end of the year, mark this end and a fresh start of the upcoming year 2019 with fun-filled moments. Get ready to enjoy, dance and have fun all night with the most happening-to-be event of the year 2018 in Navi Mumbai.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Royal Event Management</strong> promises to turn your New Year beginning into an unforgettable event with <strong>Sparkling Forest New Year Bash 2019 </strong>at <strong>Patil Farmhouse Shiravali,&nbsp;Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra</strong>, India on <strong>Mon 31st Dec 2018</strong> &amp; Tue 1st Jan 2019 from <strong>06:00 PM to 03:00 AM</strong>. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">With best DJs and thrilling night of dance and music in the rocking city, this event is surely set to make your New Year celebration immensely splendid. Let yourself groove and dance to the most happening music. Raise the toast to cheer the year passing by and welcome a new beginning with international DJ performers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This New Year bash would certainly make you hit the dance floor with a new