(47, 'Warriors Village:  One Day Picnic Spot in Gurgaon', 'warriors-village-gurgaon', 11, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you planning the weekend with friends and family? Well, there is a place that can make....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you planning the weekend with friends and family? Well, there is a place that can make your time with your dear </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">one&#39;s</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> complete fun! Warriors Village, Manesar is your destination for the next weekend where you can enjoy </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">daily</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> activities in a group. Owners of this lavish property, which is located in the outskirts of<strong>&nbsp;Delhi/ NCR</strong>, have planned many outdoor activities for<strong> adventure lovers</strong>. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Activities like <strong>ATV rides</strong>, <strong>zorbing, rock climbing, flying fox, rappelling</strong>, etc. will definitely cause an adrenaline rush. Head out for a unique adventure experience with your acquaintances to this adventure village. To make your outing even more fun, Warriors Village organizers have planned other exciting activities like pool party and camping. Give your mind and body the mush-needed refreshment with pool-side parties and gear up for the winters in style. Camping is another great idea to make your day at the <strong>Warriors Village </strong>memorable. You can accommodate in different types of camps according to your strength and experience an incredible day in a pristine </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">setup</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Both kids and adults can have a wonderful day out here with activities planned according to their tastes and preferences. Spread in the area of 15 acres, Warriors Village gives you the opportunity to spend a blissful day in a rural and cultural heritage. It&rsquo;s located just a few kilometers</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> away from the Millennium city of Gurgaon and is popular for its lush green fields and whispering winds.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>How to Reach</strong>: This charming holiday destination is located at a distance of <strong>20 KM from Rajiv Chowk Gurugram</strong>, and you will take around 30 minutes to reach here. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Timings</strong>:&nbsp; 09.30 &ndash; 05.30 Hrs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Adult (Full Day Activity + Food) &ndash; INR 1180</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Child 5 to 12 Years (Full Day Activity + Food) &ndash; INR 650</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"m