(48, 'Earthing Music Festival - New Year Party 2019', 'earthing-music-festival-jaipur', 1, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Fifth edition of Earthing Music Festival promises to give its participants an experience....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Sacred Sandal Wood Forest of Dugari Rajasthan is the ideal destination for all the free spirits, hippies, music lovers, jugglers, campers, adventurers, healers, and the brave-hearten wanderlusts. The much-awaited <strong>Earthing Music Festival 2019</strong> is finally here and will run for <strong>non-stop 40 hours </strong>among rustling leaves and whisperings winds. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Fifth edition of <strong>Earthing Music Festival</strong> promises to give its participants an experience that is way beyond just an ordinary party. It already has witnessed successful gatherings over the past and is likely to be even more exciting this time. It&rsquo;s an open-air event being organized in the sacred Shiva Valley of Dugari to captivate the visitors with lush green surroundings and the serene lake. There is also an ancestral palace, which is more than <strong>400 years old and belongs to the King Dugari.</strong> So, get ready to soak yourself in pleasant surroundings of this outstanding <strong>New Year party 2019</strong> venue.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The festival stands true to its name, as it will take you close to the four elements of the mother Earth - Water, Air, Fire &amp; Earth. You can rediscover your connection with t