(49, 'Amity Gurugram Marathon 2019 - Register Now', 'amity-gurugram-marathon', 2, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Amity Gurugram Marathon is catching the attention of both, professional runners and amateurs...</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One of the biggest sporting initiatives for the masses &ndash; <strong>Amity Gurugram Marathon</strong> is catching the attention of both, professional runners and amateurs. Till 2017, AGM was organized as a Half Marathon. Considering the enthusiasm of professional runners from across more than <strong>20 countries</strong>, the organizers have transformed the initiative into a Full Marathon. There will be many other race categories at <strong>Amity Gurugram Marathon 2019</strong> to encourage participation from the people of all age groups. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This running initiative is also helping many social organizations take their good cause to the masses and empower the underprivileged. One of the biggest marathon events in the country, AGM is also going to offer a prize money to winners in selective categories to keep them up and running. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Marathon Guidelines &amp; Regulations</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One applicant can register in only one race category, which cannot be changed after the completion of the registration process. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Registration fee is non-refundable.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Participants are not allowed to run with infants, pets or children who are below the permissible age. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">If you do not start the run at the given start time, you will not be eligible for certificates/ medals. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Participants of Full &amp; Half Marathon are advised to collect their runners&rsquo; kit/ bib in person&nbsp;from 1st &ndash; 3rd February 2019 &amp; 6th &ndash; 7th February 2019. </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Race Categories</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Full Marathon &ndash; 42.2 KM</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(18 Years of Age &amp; Above)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Half Marathon &ndash; 21.1 KM</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(14 Years of Age &amp; Above)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">10 KM Run</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(12 years of age &amp; above)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">5 KM Run</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(12 years of age &amp; above)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">5 KM Kids Run </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(Age between 06 years to 12 years)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Senior Citizen Run</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(Age 60 years &amp; above)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can register individually or opt for the bulk registration option if you want to run for the good cause with your own gang of running enthusiasts. Click on<strong>&nbsp;&quot;Official&nbsp;Ticket&nbsp;URL&quot; </strong>button to register today! Never miss an opportunity to run for a charity and good health!</span></span></p>', '2019-02-10', '2019-02-10', '04:00:00', '09:30:00', '1543859257.jpg', '1543812241.jpg', 35, '', 'https://www.goeventz.com/event/amity-gurugram-marathon/83440?utm_source=Festeve-mantra&utm_medium=Website&utm_campaign=Festeve-mantra-website-event', 'http://www.amitymarathon.com/default.asp', 'https://www.facebook.com/amitygurugrammarathon', 'https://twitter.com/amitygurugramm', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/amitymarathon/', '', '', '', 0, 594, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-03 11:44:01', '2018-12-04 00:47:37'),
