(52, 'New Party Year 2019 Ft Olly Esse- Le Meridien Hotel, Bengaluru', 'new-year-party-2019-olly-esse-bengaluru', 5, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Partying to celebrate the new year is a customary ritual as it marks the fresh start and welcome.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Partying to celebrate the new year is a customary ritual as it marks the fresh start and welcome note to the upcoming days and months. Each year-end transitions to new aspirations and hopes and you must celebrate it the grand way to yell out the happiness with the grand night.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To make your celebration more happening and add more spice, fun, and enjoyment,&nbsp; <strong>SIA Events and Entertainment</strong> awaits for you to join the talk-of-the-year event <strong>PARTY YEAR 2019 Ft Olly Esse- Le Meridien Hotel</strong> in Bengaluru. At Bangalore&rsquo;s finest 5-star venue, <strong>The Sugar Factory, Le Meridien Hotel, Bengaluru</strong><strong> </strong>on <strong>Mon, 31st Dec 2018 </strong>and<strong> Tue, 1st Jan 2019</strong> the NYE extravaganza celebration of the new year arrival will commence at <strong>06:00 PM</strong> onwards and last until <strong>12:15 AM</strong>. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can choose to buy for Couple, VIP, Female Stag or Male Stag entry with friends, family or circles and witness the arrival of the new year the most festive way.</span></strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"fo