></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Terrific stage setting, music and light settings by Agnus</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Security arrangements empowered with bouncers</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Don&rsquo;t wait to lose your chance to become a part of this spectacle celebration and buy your passes now. Click on &quot;<strong>Official Ticket URL</strong>&quot; button&nbsp;and grab the ticket to the most entertaining event of the year.</span></span></p>', '2018-12-31', '2019-01-01', '18:00:00', '00:30:00', '1544078145.jpg', '1544078145.jpg', 39, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/new-year-party-2019?acode=aAcuPF', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/siaentertainments/posts/?ref=page_internal', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 237, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-06 13:35:45', '2019-01-01 13:35:16'),
(53, 'HT Palate Fest Mumbai 2019: Food & Music Festival', 'ht-palate-fest-delhi-mumbai-2019', 3, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">HT Palate Fest is one of the most popular fests in Mumbai and is here again with its 1st&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">edition on.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">HT Palate Fest is one of the most popular fests in Mumbai and is here again with its 1st&nbsp;edition on popular demand. This time, the platform for this fest will be <strong>Mahalaxmi Racecourse, Royal Western India Turf, Mahalakshmi, Mumbai</strong>&nbsp;where foodies from all corners of the city will gather for a sweet and savoury gourmet bash.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">And, there will be stalls from the city&rsquo;s favourite food brands like:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Adya Organics</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Baba Rolls</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Brew House Ice Tea</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cane Juicery</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Dope Coffee Roasters</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Edwins Milkshake</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">El Marcado</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Farzi&nbsp;Cafe</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Fat Lulu&#39;s</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Giani</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Hillcart&nbsp;Tales</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ITC Grand Central</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Keventers Milkshake</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Punjab Grill</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Waffle House</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Woodside Burger Shop and many more</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>HT Palate Fest</strong> will offer a tantalizing range of food comprising of <strong>Thai, Italian, Continental, Chinese, American, French and Indian cuisines </strong>from leading names in the culinary space and will bring together the countries finest restaurants and talented chefs such as Harpal Singh Sokhi of Turban Tadka and chef of the year 2017- Nishant Choubey on 19th of January. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">On a concluding day, Master Chef India&#39;s winner- <strong>Ripu Daman Handa</strong> and </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\">Adtiri</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong> Govitrikar</strong>, a culinary chef and a psychologist will embellish the event on <strong>20th of January</strong>. Additionally, the renowned and talented Bollywood actress&nbsp;<strong>Shilpa Shetty Kundra</strong>&nbsp;will be joining us on 20th&nbsp;January 2019 to share her expertise on health, fitness and her love for food.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">On 19th Jan the<strong> Indian rock band- Euphoria</strong> will dazzle the venue with their scintillating performance. On 20th Jan, witness the <strong>vibrant musician, American rapper and record producer- Bohemia</strong> who will set the stage on fire with his performance. It is surely going to be a lip-smacking and sumptuous feast for residents of Mumbai.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Remember that the entry to the Fest is <strong>Free</strong>! </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Be ready for an all-encompassing Food &amp; Music Festival loved by families and youth alike. This gastronomic adventure will bring together a wide range of chefs and cooking sessions to treat you to a culinary experience&nbsp;like never before.</span></span></p>', '2019-01-19', '2019-01-20', '11:30:00', '22:30:00', '1545027906.jpg', '1544256119.jpg', 40, '', 'http://www.palatefest.com/', 'http://www.palatefest.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/htpalatefest/', 'https://twitter.com/PalateFest?lang=en', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/htpalatefest/', '', '', '', 0, 1325, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-08 15:01:59', '2019-01-17 13:52:25'),
(54, 'Kasol Music Festival V3 2018-19 - New Year Party', 'kasol-music-festival-2018-19-new-year-party', 1, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Music, masti, and celebration make the perfect blend to make new year welcoming a great affair...</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Music, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Masti</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">, and celebration make the perfect blend to make new year welcoming a great affair and greeting the new beginning in the lap of nature make it mesmerizing. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Travamigo</strong> is kicking off a not-to-be-missed music festival to mark the beginning of new year in style at the only 5-star property in Kasol,<strong> The Himalayan Village, Kullu</strong> from <strong>Sat 29th Dec 2018 </strong>to <strong>Wed 2nd Jan 2019</strong>. This one-of-its-kind festival would let you witness a distinct fusion of nature from </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Himalayas</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> and musical madness and mayhem of the sky-kissing ranges loaded with natural beauty and humming of beautiful creatures. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can choose to register for the event with day passes to attend the festival on day-basis o