(56, 'New Year\'s Eve Bollywood Dhamaka: NY Party 2019', 'new-year-eve-bollywood-dhamaka', 5, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To make you rock like Bollywood stars and make the most of fun-filled entertaining new year celebration....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Bollywood is an inescapable stage that fascinates people of all ages. Bollywood music especially dance numbers add to every celebration and take the fun to the next level with authentic beats and rhythm. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To make you rock like Bollywood stars and make the most of fun-filled entertaining new year celebration, <strong>Beat The Beats Dance Academy </strong>invites you for the <strong>New Year&#39;s Eve Bollywood Dhamaka: New Year Party 2019 </strong>on <strong>December 31, 2018, </strong>at <strong>Beat The Beats Fitness and Dance Academy, Gurugram</strong>. You can now shake a leg on the zippy Bollywood dance songs with entirely Bollywood-like setup and infrastructure.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This captivating Bollywood celebration would enthrall you with the musically themed environment, alluring dance floors and what&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">not</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> that reflects the Bollywood presentation. This new year party would leave you strikingly thrilled and entertained with lots of memorable moments to rejoice in the