(57, 'Kitty Su – New Year 2019 Party at The Lalit, Delhi', 'new-year-party-2019-kitty-su-the-lalit-delhi', 5, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get ready to feel fabulous on the night of 31<sup>st</sup> December by being at Kitty Su with your pals....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Where are you partying on the New Year Eve? If it&rsquo;s not at <strong>Kitty Su in Central Delhi</strong>, then it may not be as exciting as you want. Kitty Su is one of the popular nightclubs in India and is your ideal destination for the most awesome night of the year. Get ready to feel fabulous on the night of 31<sup>st</sup> December by being at Kitty Su with your pals, partner or that special friend. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The New Year eve at Kitty Su is going to be all about decked up ladies accompanying their men who will be all suited up for the most special night. Come, witness the amazing New Year party at one of the best nightclubs in India. <strong>To make you feel fabulous, the place will be having kittens on the saxophone, men in high heels, golden shower boys, and many more surprises. </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This place hosts a range of parties throughout the year, and they are ready to take the celebration a notch higher on New Year Eve. <strong>From Electro to Pop, from House to Disco, this place is truly the shrine for urban music lovers</strong>. And, the aesthetic opulence and artistic innovation at this place will lift your mood instantly. If classy is all you desire, <strong>Kitty Su i