(59, 'Winter Delhi Half Marathon 2019: Run For Life', 'winter-delhi-half-marathon-2019', 2, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Winter Delhi Half Marathon 2019 invites participation from all those fitness enthusiasts.....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After the success of <strong>Winter Delhi Half Marathon,</strong> the <strong>Run for Life Foundation</strong> is back again with an event that&rsquo;s even bigger and better! Winter Delhi Half Marathon 2019 invites participation from all those fitness enthusiasts and amateurs who want to contribute to the social cause of providing education to the economically unprivileged section of the society. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Marathon also intends to create awareness for long distance running among the youth of the city, who need to challenge their own limits when it comes to fitness. Drudgeries of the mundane life often make them ignorant about their health, and this is the ideal event to buckle up for fitness. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Event Date</strong>: 6 January 2018</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Last Date of registration: </strong>1 January 2018</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Race Categories</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: