(63, 'Air Heroes Half Marathon 2019, Delhi', 'air-heroes-half-marathon-delhi', 2, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This marathon also aims at creating awareness about running among the youth of this country....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">How often we get to do something for our brave soldiers? Now, you have a chance to encourage India soldiers by participating in <strong>Air Heroes Half Marathon 2019</strong>, organized by <strong>Grow on Foundation</strong>. It will be a race to motivate Indian soldiers happening on 13 January 2019, just two days before the Indian Army Day (that is on 15 January).</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The work done by Indian soldiers is incredible, and this will be our gesture to thank them for protecting the borders of India. Not just that! Whenever there is any natural calamity or any man-made disorder in the country, the army is always there to bring the situation under control. So, we all should participate in the <strong>Air Heroes Half Marathon</strong> and show our solitude.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This marathon also aims at creating awareness about running among the youth of this country. People from all age groups can come together and participate in the marathon as a significant step towards healthy living. And the money collected through registration for the marathon will go for a social cause, that is, supporting economically underprivileged section of the society. The money will be spent in helping them in their education and working for their upliftment.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Race Categories</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\">&middot;</span><u><strong>21 Km Run</strong></u></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&uuml;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Registration fee: INR 1100</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings\">&uuml;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Age: 18 to 45 years</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Symbol\">&middot;</span><u><strong>21 km Senior Citizen Run</strong></u></span></s