(72, 'India International Jewellery Show 2019', 'india-international-jewellery-show-2019', 10, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">India International Jewellery Show (IIJS Signature) is the country&rsquo;s renowned jewellery show that showcases....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">India International Jewellery Show (IIJS Signature) is the country&rsquo;s renowned </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> show that showcases the best designs and collections by leading manufacturers in the country. The focus of the event is to bring forth the craftsmanship of </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> designers and manufacturers in India. With over 870 exhibitors and 15K visitors expected at the event, the IIJS Signature is ready to revitalize jewellery trends in 2019. &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The event provides a great sourcing opportunity </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">to</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> visitors who also get a chance to develop strong connections with other participants. They can meet many new suppliers and have discussions with </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> manufacturers about their new designs. IIJS Signature has gained much prestige over the years, as it&rsquo;s the ideal platform for participants to keep abreast of the latest happenings i