eir expertise. With India being a major player in the global </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">jewellery segment, the Fair is likely to bring forth some of the best international trends. It will provide a complete overview of the work done by leading designers and niche artisans to leave a strong mark in the jewellery</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> segment. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>', '2019-02-10', '2019-02-13', '10:00:00', '19:00:00', '1546184997.jpg', '1546184997.jpg', 57, '', 'https://iijs-signature.org/domestic_user_registration.php', 'https://iijs-signature.org/index.php', 'https://www.facebook.com/GJEPC', 'https://twitter.com/GJEPCIndia', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 194, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-30 22:49:57', '2018-12-30 23:33:40'),
(73, 'Index International Trade Fair 2019: Delhi | Mumbai', 'index-international-trade-fair-2019', 10, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Index International Trade Fair is India&rsquo;s largest commercial platform for architects, interior designers...</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Index International Trade Fair is India&rsquo;s largest commercial platform for architects, interior designers, procurement experts and more. This event is held every year in India and it brings together decision makers from the architecture and interior design segment at a single platform. <strong>The 31st edition</strong> of this trade fair will be held in <strong>Mumbai and New Delhi </strong>soon and is already getting registrations from both buyers and suppliers in this field. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Popular Categories</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Furniture</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Kitchen &amp; Appliances</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Office Furniture</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Furnishings</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Hardware</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Materials</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Art &amp; Artefacts</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Suppliers and retailers can book their own stall to exhibit their products among visitors at the event. They can either opt for the Stand Option with Shell Scheme or Mezzanine Structure or take the Bare Space and build their own booth structure. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Why Exhibit at Index?</span></strong></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You will gain access to the Index Fairs &lsquo;Promotional Plan&rsquo;, and enjoy the presence in key visitor groups for a year. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can enter into the prosperous domestic markets through promotions during the fair.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can access year-round promotions, focused B2B support and media partnerships through Index Fairs.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can benefit from the Index Fair&rsquo;s partnership with The Times of India and IFJ (The Indian Review of World Furniture, Interiors &amp; Design).</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Click on &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site</strong>&quot; button to Visitor Registration &amp;&nbsp;and get free entry at Index.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">For Book your stall: <a href=\"https://www.indexfairs.com/book-your-stall/\">Click here</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What are The Visitor Benefits?</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Witness international brands, designs and the best industry practices</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Connect with international buyers and sellers</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Network with over 300 quality exhibitors</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get new products and collections</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Be a part of knowledge forums and gain valuable insights</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Experience the latest advancements in your industry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Be a part of new product launches</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Exhibition Days</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Mumbai: (1, 2, 3, 4 May 2019)</span></strong></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">New Delhi: (2, 3, 4 August 2019)</span></strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Over the years, Index has witnessed many national and international players reaching new heights in terms of profits. Designers, architects, builders and procurement experts from India and across the world attend this event to create new business opportunities. At the 30<sup>th</sup> edition, more than 30, 000 visitors attended the event, and this year it&rsquo;s going to be even better. So, what you are still waiting? Register for this event today!</span></span></p>', '2019-05-01', '2019-05-04', '10:00:00', '18:00:00', '1546235447.jpg', '1546235447.jpg', 58, '', 'https://www.indexfairs.com/book-your-stall/', 'https://www.indexfairs.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/indexfairs/', 'https://twitter.com/indextradefairs', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/umg-index-tradefairs-pvt.-ltd./', '', '', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/umg-index-tradefairs-pvt.-ltd./', '', 0, 221, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2018-12-31 12:50:47', '2018-12-31 12:50:47');
