(74, '3 Days Agile Coach Certification Program, Pune', 'agile-coach-certification-pune', 7, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Agile Coaching Workshop is a three-day certification program, which is directed towards making.....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The <strong>Agile Coaching Workshop</strong> is a <strong>three-day certification progra</strong>m, which is directed towards making the participants more efficient in Agile Coaching roles and responsibilities. The workshop will cover different aspects of Agile </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Coaching</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">, such as mentoring, coaching, facilitating, teaching and developing an Agile Coaching mindset.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This workshop is designed by the experts in Agile Coaching who will help participants learn the nuances of Agile Coaching with discussions and role plays. Also, relevant videos will be shown to help learners have an in-depth understanding of Agile Coaching concepts.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Experts at the workshop will pay special focus on developing skills for self-awareness, servant leadership, response-ability, powerful questioning, active listening and managing team dysfunctions</strong>. Learners at the workshop will discover the tricks to build high-performance agile teams by using the right set of tools and techniques. Aspiring Agile Coaches will learn to perform even in complex environments.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>The Course Outline:</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coaching mindset, role </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> responsibilities</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coaching boundaries, agile coaching alliance</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coach as Professional Agile Coach</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coach as Teacher</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coach as Mentor</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coaching models, tools and techniques</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Building High-Performance Teams</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The Coaching Stance</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Coaching Leadership Teams</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coaching Career Path</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Who Should Attend:</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Practicing or Aspiring Agile Coaches</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Change Agents</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Leaders Working with Teams</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Scrum Masters or Product Owners</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Project Managers and Team Leaders</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Know More About the Workshop:</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You will get &lsquo;<strong>ICAgile Certified Professional in Agile Coaching (ICP-ACC)</strong>&rsquo; certificate after attending the three-day workshop. There will be no exam after the workshop, and the certificate has lifetime validity with no fee for renewal.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Workshop Period</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Friday, 1st Feb 2019 - Sunday, 3rd Feb 2019</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">09:00 AM to 06:00 PM</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Last Date of Registration</strong>: 1st Feb 2019</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Registrations Fees:</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Early Bird: INR 27000</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Regular: INR 29990</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Combo (SAFe Agilist and ICP - ACC): INR 60000</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Combo (PMI-ACP and ICP-ACC): INR 35000</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site</strong>&quot; Button&nbsp;below to register now. By registering for this certification course, you will also get access to Agile Book Library and Book Club Sessions. Also, you will get Agile career counseling and referrals for better career opportunities.</span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-02-01', '2019-02-03', '09:00:00', '17:00:00', '1546507425.jpg', '1546507425.jpg', 59, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/agile-coach-certification-pune-february-2019?acode=aAcuPF', 'https://www.scaleupconsultants.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ScaleUpConsultants/', 'https://twitter.com/ScaleUpPune/', '', '', 'https://plus.google.com/+ScaleUpConsultants1', '', '', 0, 192, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-03 16:23:45', '2019-01-03 16:25:47'),
(75, '8th Edition  - Delhi Jewellery & Gem Fair 2019', 'delhi-jewellery-and-gem-fair-2019', 10, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Delhi Jewellery and Gem Fair (DJGF) is one of the most popular international jewellery trade shows....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Delhi Jewellery and Gem Fair</strong> (DJGF) is one of the most popular international jewellery trade shows, which is happening at Pragati Maidan New Delhi in September. The eighth edition of DJGF will saw a glittery display of exquisite </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> pieces from <strong>700 plus top-notch brands.</strong> Along with renowned brands, even dignitaries from the </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> trade will attend the fair to give visitors an insight into the latest trends in the industry of glitz and glitter.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Traders from different parts of the country, such as Punjab, Haryana, Rajasthan, Uttar Pradesh </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> Maharashtra will mark their presence at the biggest </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> and gemstone sourcing destination. The place is a hub for </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">j<strong>ewellery</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> manufacturers, </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> wholesalers, retailers, importers and exporters who are interested in procuring diamond, gemstone and other precious </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>.</strong> Also, gemstone peal suppliers &amp; distributors, precious metal &amp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> mounting traders and suppliers, and public trade organizations will come together at one platform to connect and grow their business.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">One of the key highlights of this Fair will be seminars organized by gem &amp; </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jewellery</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> experts to help visitors understand different </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">gemmological</span><span style=\"f