style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Event Date</strong>: 28th Sep - 30th Sep 2019</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Time</strong>: 10:00 am to 6:00 pm</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Registration for visitors &amp; exhibitors will open soon.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">With more than 5000 estimated visitors and 150 exhibitors, the Delhi Jewellery &amp; Gem Fair is going to be bigger and better this year. Ready to make your move?</span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-09-28', '2019-09-30', '10:00:00', '18:00:00', '1546538762.jpg', '1546538762.jpg', 61, '', 'https://delhi.jewelleryfair.in/', 'https://delhi.jewelleryfair.in/', '', 'https://twitter.com/ubm', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ubm-plc/', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCHRidj-Yn6j_EmkjIJacOmA', '', 0, 226, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-04 01:06:02', '2019-01-04 01:12:01'),
(76, 'LED Expo Mumbai 2019: Lighting Innovations', 'led-expo-mumbai-2019', 10, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Expo is a popular name in the lighting arena, providing endless opportunities to counterparts....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">India has a huge industry potential in LED as a futuristic technology that has taken the lighting world by storm. And, LED Expo has recognized the scope of LED in the lighting industry at the right time. It&rsquo;s the only show in the country which encompasses the entire possibilities of the revolutionary LED trend. This Expo is all about LED products and technologies, which attract thousands of exhibitors and visitors every year. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>LED Expo</strong> is a popular name in the lighting arena, providing endless opportunities to counterparts in this field. It provides a platform where they can exchange knowledge and discuss innovations in this industry. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Over</strong> <strong>200 hundred exhibitors are expected to put their stall at the LED Expo, which is happening in May 2019. Also, there are likely to be 12K visitors at the LED Expo to explore the recent trends in </strong></span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">LED</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> industry. </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Product Groups</span></span></strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LEDs</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Applications &amp; Lighting</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Lighting Products</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Signage &amp; Displays</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Components &amp; Raw Materials</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Manufacturing Equipment/ Machinery &amp; Allied Products</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Drivers &amp; Power Supply</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Expo Date</strong>: 9 &mdash; 11 May 2019</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Expo has always provided business opportunities to counterparts of the LED industry. Exhibitors at the event successfully generate qualified leads, which they can further nurture to boost their sales conversions. Customers come in large numbers at the Expo, as exhibitors there caters to their needs perfectly. This is the ideal platform for LED industry </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">stakeholders,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> and contributes significantly to the industry growth. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The entry is free for business and trade visitors. To Register for the Expo, you need to <strong>download</strong> the Application Form from their official website. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Application Fee for Exhibitors</span></span></strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Standard package (min 9 sqm) </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&euro; 290 / ₹ 12,500 + 18% GST</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Raw space (min 21 sqm) </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&euro; 250 / ₹ 12,000 + 18% GST</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><u><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Who Must Attend This Expo?</strong></span></span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Architects &amp; interior designers</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Lighting engineers/ designers</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Construction &amp; real estate companies</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dealers and distributors of lighting and LED products</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Engineers from Automotive Industry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Building contractors &amp; project management consultants</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Professionals operating hotels, mall, restaurants, office &amp; commercial establishments</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Public Works Department (PWD), Central Public Works Department (CPWD) and municipal corporations</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Officials from ministries of power, new &amp; renewable energy, environment &amp; urban development and railway.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">LED Expo showcases the best of LED industry in terms of the latest products and technologies. It&rsquo;s time for the stakeholders of this industry to step up their </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">game,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> and showcase their expertise. The Expo promises to offer an outstanding experience to both visitors and exhibitors.</span></span></p>', '2019-05-09', '2019-05-11', '10:30:00', '18:00:00', '1546669050.jpg', '1546669050.jpg', 60, '', 'https://led-expo-mumbai.in.messefrankfurt.com/mumbai/en/planning-preparation/exhibitors.html', 'https://led-expo-mumbai.in.messefrankfurt.com/mumbai/en.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/ledexpoindia/', 'https://twitter.com/LEDExpoIndia', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ledexpoindia/', 'https://www.instagram.com/theledexpoindia/', '', '', '', 0, 228, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-05 13:17:30', '2019-01-05 13:17:30'),
(77, 'Basic Photography Workshop - Ameenpur Lake', 'photography-workshop-Photofoundation-hyderabad', 7, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">It&rsquo;s a chance for you to learn new photography skills and be an expert in this field. At the Photofoundation...</span></span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Is photography your passion? It&rsquo;s a chance for you to learn new photography skills and be an expert in this field. At the <strong>Photofoundation workshop</strong>, you will get to learn the basics of photography and a lot more than that. From understanding different camera functions to using them in different scenarios, you will surely enhance your photography skills at this workshop. Founders and organizations of this photography workshop provide&nbsp;lifetime subscription, under which you can attend all their workshops as and when scheduled.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">During the workshop, you will get strategic training in photography, so that you can continue with it as a profession. Photography experts at the workshop will demonstrate how to use different camera functions with changing lighting conditions across different photography genres. Also, you can join their exclusive WhatsApp groups to know more about their upcoming workshops. By being a part of the active photography community of Hyderabad city, you can also get online assistance for using different camera features online.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Key learning at the upcoming workshop will be of the &lsquo;when, why &amp; which&rsquo; of photography real-time scenarios. Also, you can discuss with experts about all important photography objectives.</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">If you have any doubt after the workshop, or you are facing any trouble while capturing any moment, you can attend their other lined-up workshops for free. You can also be a part of live photography sessions to acquire new expertise. &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">They provide camera at the workshop for free, in case you forget to carry your own or the batter of your camera is low. Thus, you can rest assured that there will be no interruption in your enthusiasm for learning photography skills.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Event Date</strong>: Saturday, 2nd Feb 2019 | 07:00 AM to 09:00 AM GST</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Photofoundation Lifetime Subscription Charge</strong>: INR 2000</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site</strong>&quot; Button&nbsp;below to register today. It&rsquo;s an amazing opportunity to live your passion for photography and be a part of an ongoing learning activity.</span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-02-02', '2019-02-02', '07:00:00', '09:00:00', '1546682252.jpg', '1546682252.jpg', 62, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/basics-of-photography-ameenpur-lake-february-2nd?acode=aAcuPF', 'https://photofountain.portfoliobox.io/', 'https://www.facebook.com/PhotofountainGetTrainedToCaptureAnything/', 'https://twitter.com/photofountain', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/photofountain/?originalSubdomain=in', 'https://instagram.com/photofountainsta/', 'https://plus.google.com/100233218945806957072', '', '', 0, 150, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-05 16:57:32', '2019-01-05 16:57:32'),
(78, '2 Days Ethereum BlockChain Hands-On Training', 'blockchain-training-bangalore', 7, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Hands-on blockchain training is going to happen in Bangalore soon. It will be a two-day training...</span></span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Hands-on blockchain training is going to happen in Bangalore soon. It will be a two-day training in February with the emphasis on building and deploying IoT and Blockchain solutions for different business functions.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">It&rsquo;s essential training for those who want to give a boost to their career. Along with professionals, even corporate leaders can attend this training to learn how blockchain and IoT can transform their business processes for better.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Key Learnings at the Training:</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Creating cryptocurrency token</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Building cryptocurrency wallet and exchange</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Create Blockchain Private Network on platforms like Azure &amp; AWS</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Building Blockchain for supply-chain solutions</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Learning Solidity Programming Language, Chaincode, Java </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> Cotlin, so that you can write smart contracts.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can also build and deploy decentralized applications by using Hyperledger fabric, Stellar, R3 Corda and Ethereum.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The training is being organized by Pingala Software, who hold years of experience in providing training to corporates and professionals. They are also providing Blockchain &amp; IoT training for quite a long time now, and are a trusted name in this field.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Event Date</strong>: Saturday, 2nd Feb 2019 - Sunday, 3rd Feb 2019</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Event Time</strong>: 09:30 AM to 05:30 PM IST</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Registration Fee</strong>: INR 22000</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site</strong>&quot; Button&nbsp;below to register today. Along with Blockchain, you will also get to learn about Ethereum, Solidity, Truffle </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">and</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> Web3js. Don&rsquo;t give it a second thought! It&rsquo;s an amazing opportunity to acquire new skills and grow in your career.</span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-02-02', '2019-02-03', '09:30:00', '17:30:00', '1546685223.jpg', '1546685223.jpg', 63, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/blockchain-2-days-hands-on-training-in-bangalore-02-and-03-feb-2019?acode=aAcuPF', 'https://pingalasoftware.com/index.php', 'https://www.facebook.com/PingalaSoftware/', 'https://twitter.com/pingalasoftware', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pingala-software-india-pvt-ltd/', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1OT9S-w9WPGdiRGOFk31_w', '', 0, 169, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-05 17:47:03', '2019-01-05 17:47:03'),
(79, 'Indian Education Congress & Awards 2019', 'indian-education-congress-and-awards-2019', 6, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Indian Educational Congress is an event, where pioneers and trailblazers of the Indian and Global education....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">As we progress further into the vision of <strong>Digital India</strong>, education is a key sector where technology is playing a key role. Emerging virtual environments and other advancements are helping educators reach the remotest areas and helping people learn and grow.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Indian Educational Congress</strong> is an event, where pioneers and trailblazers of the Indian and Global education fraternity will come together to share their ideas and thoughts in a peer-to-peer setting. The final goal of this congregation would be to explore ways in which the education sector can continue to expand and use technology to grow.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This is the <strong>9<sup>th</sup> edition</strong> of this event and it&rsquo;s an event that should be attended by anyone who seeks to understand how education can not only change the </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">world,</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> but the role individuals can play in this process. Some of the most prominent educators, corporate gurus and entrepreneurs will be at the event, and you will learn from truly the best of the bunch.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">It&rsquo;s a 2-day event that will be held on 12-13<sup>th</sup> February 2019, at the JW Marriott Hotel, New Delhi.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Who Should Attend?</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Formal &amp; Informal Educational Stakeholders Including CEOs / Directors / Principals / Deans and Senior Management</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Suppliers &amp; Allied Industry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Corporate, Franchisors &amp; Franchisees</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Associations, Agencies &amp; Media</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Education Ministries and Councils (Regional &amp; International)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Investors, NBFC, Micro-finance Companies into Micro-Finance with focus on Education Sector</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What Will Be The Key Takeaways Of The Conference?</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Understanding how technology is transforming the education industry</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Updates on the latest advances in the field of education</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Evaluate and compare the right growth plan for your education enterprise</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Identify efficiencies and measurable outcomes coming to the classroom</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Keep tabs on Public-Private Partnerships (PPP) and government investments</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Share the room with the biggest audience of policymakers, contractors, architects, consultants and many more</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Get a modern outlook on curriculum, programme delivery, and training</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Discover the importance of marketing and getting it right both at the national and institutional level</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Financing education deals - where to find liquidity?</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">New methodology on quality assurance and school improvement</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To register for the event, click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site&quot; </strong>button<strong>.&nbsp;</strong>Education, Innovation, Entrepreneurship- The three pillars that will be celebrated at the event.</span> </span></p>', '2019-02-12', '2019-02-13', '09:30:00', '18:30:00', '1546688505.jpg', '1546688505.jpg', 7, '', 'http://www.educationcongress.org/conference_registration.php?utm_source=Festeve-mantra&utm_medium=conference-category&utm_campaign=Festeve-mantra-website-event', 'http://www.educationcongress.org/', 'https://www.facebook.com/FranchiseIndiaMedia/', 'https://twitter.com/FranchiseIndia', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/franchiseindia_/?hl=en', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/FranchiseIndia', 'Speakers', 0, 258, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-05 18:41:45', '2019-01-05 20:14:34');
