(86, 'Bungee Jumping in Rishikesh with Jumping Heights', 'bungee-jumping-rishikesh-with-jumping-heights', 11, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you an adrenaline junkie looking for your next adventure fix? Do you want to have an adventure....</span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you an adrenaline junkie looking for your next adventure fix? Do you want to have an adventure that you can brag about for the rest of your life? Well, in that case, there&rsquo;s something we want you to go for.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Go Bungee Jumping at Rishikesh and have an adventure that will last you a lifetime!</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Bungee jumping</strong> is not for the weak of heart but it&rsquo;s damn well worth it. Supervised by professionals, this will be an activity you won&rsquo;t want to miss when you&rsquo;re in Rishikesh. Nestled between the lower Himalayas, the jump will give you a pristine view of the mighty mountains while your body pumps adrenaline through your veins. And if this didn&rsquo;t psych you enough, this is India&rsquo;s highest </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">bungy</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> at a height of 83 meters.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The best part- it&rsquo;s the closest thing you feel to a superhero as you shoot through the sky and head down. Remember that scene in the Avengers when Iron Man helps Captain America arrest Loki, and he makes a superhero landing. Well, this is exactly that (minus the super-suit, obviously).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Age- Minimum 12 yrs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Weight- Minimum 40 kg, Maximum 110 kg</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Inclusions</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Jumping Gear</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Dare to Jump Certificate</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;VE GOT GUTS&rdquo; badge on completion of jump</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Things To Carry</strong></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Sports Shoes</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Due to its extreme nature, this sport is not suitable for people with the following medical conditions</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Back or Neck injuries</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Recent Fracture</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Any Dislocation</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">High Blood Pressure</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Asthma</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Neurological Disorders</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Epilepsy</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Heart Conditions</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Pregnancy</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Osteoporosis</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To make a booking, click on the <strong>&quot;Official 