(87, 'Agile Coach Certification Workshop (ICP-ACC), Mumbai', 'agile-coach-certification-mumbai', 7, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Agile Coaching Workshop (ICP-ACC) is a 3-day training workshop, designed to help managers and....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Are you struggling to make your talented team work together? Then this workshop is perfect for you.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Agile Coaching Workshop (ICP-ACC)</strong> is a 3-day training workshop, designed to help managers and leaders in learning the principle of agile teams. It&rsquo;ll be held from <strong>Friday, 22nd Feb 2019 to Sunday, 24th Feb 2019 at Practice Agile Solutions, Powai, Chandivali, Mumbai</strong>. During this training program, you&rsquo;ll learn the skills needed to develop professional agile coaching skills and understand the difference between different aspects of Agile Coaching like teaching, facilitating, mentoring and coaching, to develop the right agile coaching mindset.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You should attend this program to learn core professional agile coaching skills such as self-awareness, response-ability, servant leadership, active listening, powerful questioning and managing 