(88, 'Winter Spiti Snow Drive - 7 nights/8 days', 'winter-spiti-snow-drive-package', 4, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Take an 8-day 7-night road trip through Spiti Valley in winter, an experience you&rsquo;ll never ever forget....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>A Snow-Laden Drive Through Spiti- Winter Spiti Snow Drive</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">-25&deg;C, tarmac roads covered in snow, chilling wind all around and most importantly, the best ride of your life!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Take an 8-day 7-night road trip through Spiti Valley in winter, an experience you&rsquo;ll never ever forget.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This trip will take you through the coldest and least-inhabited parts of the upper Himalayas: Narkanda- Pabbar Valley-Sangla Valley-Tabo-Kunzum-Kaza-Langza and Kye Monastery-Kalpa-Kinnaur</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You&rsquo;ll experience the nomads and local tribes that inhabit this place, drive through remote land with pristine views to keep you company &amp; make some memories that will last you forever.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Since this is a winter ride, participants must be physically fit and well acclimatised to colder conditions.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day 1: Arrival at the Narkanda</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Our Camps at &nbsp;Narkanda, awaits your arrival, followed by check in. Enjoy the rest of the evening with bonfire, music and choice of Bar-b-Q on request . followed by dinner.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Day 2: Narkanda- Pabbar Valley ( Chansal Pass) 110 Km</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After breakfast and a briefing session brace yourself for bumpy snow drive Further down we will visit Chanshal through narrow and snow-clad roads with alternative views every now and then. Overnight camping with bonfire and music.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day 3: Pabbar Valley to Sangla Valley (219km)</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Behold yourself for the most strenuous drive today as the roads will be snow laden and stony, once been called the most dangerous roads on the planet. As we drive alongside the satuj river to enter the beautiful Sangla Valley of Kinnaur. Overnight homestay, be prepared for some kinnauri surprises.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Day 4- Sangla Valley to Tabo/ (178km)</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\nAfter visiting Chitkul (The last village of India situated at 3500 Meters) with breath-taking views alongside Baspa River if the route is accessible of course, we will visit Tabo after clicking some pictures of the mesmerizing crystal clear Nako Lake, en route we will also cross Sumdo check-post from where the International Border of Tibet (Formally Republic of China) is merely 12 kilometres away. Overnight at Guest House in Tabo.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day 5- Tabo-Kunzum-Kaza-Langza and Kye Monastery</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After breakfast and monastery visit we will head for Kunzum Pass which will be covered under a thick blanket of snow. We won&#39;t be able to reach the mighty Kunzum at 4800 Meters but still, it&rsquo;s going be to be an adventurous feat as we will our test our driving skills under heaps of snow. If road permits we will visit Kibber and Kye Monastery on our return. Overnight stay in Kaza<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong>Day 6 Kaza - Kalpa (196km)</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Today we drive back towards Kinnaur. We will stay in a hotel/guest house today with an amazing view of snow-covered massif in front of us. Today we will retrace our wheels back to Kinnaur, however this time we will visit Recong Peo (administrative capital of Kinnaur) and Kalpa. Enjoy the mighty views of the holy kinner Kailash from Kalpa, visit suicide point, Roghi Village. Overnight stay in a guest house.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day 7 Kinnaur(Kalpa)- Narkanda (162km)</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">We will return back to our camps in Narkanda after this amazing feat which not many of the adventurists can claim to achieve in these months of the year of Winters. We will celebrate the amazing feat as a party awaits for us in Narkanda. Evening enjoys dance, music and bonfire at our camps.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Day 8 Narkanda- Shimla and Back&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Time to head back home with tonnes of beautiful memories.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Inclusions</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">3 Meals (Breakfast, Lunch &amp; Dinner Per Day)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Stay in Twin to Multiple Sharing Basis</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Lead Car and Backup Car</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">4x4 Car Bolero Campers</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Boarding &amp; Lodging</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Housekeeping and Kitchen Van</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Camping Tents</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">(Twin Sharing) with Mattress</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Portable Toilets with Toiletries</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Medical Kit (First Aid Only)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Things to Carry</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Antiseptic Alcohol-Based Hand Wash (Essential).</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Sun Block (Essential): A High Factor Is Strongly Recommended.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Sleeping Bag (Essential): Mattress Will Be Provided Every Night, Please Bring Your Own Sleeping Bag for Nights In The Remote Locations.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Light Weight Yet Warm Clothing Is Absolutely Necessary as You Will Be Travelling Into Sub-Zero Temperatures.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A Lightweight 2-3 Season Bag Is Recommended.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Wash Bag, Scarf / Bandanna, Caps (To Protect Neck, Ears and Head), Fleece / Pullover, Towel, Snow Boots, Casual Trousers And</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Bungee Cords...</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">And Finally, Ear Plugs - To Protect Against Snoring RoomMates!</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Total Price for 7N/8 Days &ndash; Rs 19500 + 5% GST (Includes 4x4 vehicles, Fuel, all meals and stay).<br />\r\nFor personal vehicles and motorbikes &ndash; Price is Rs 14000/- + 5% GST (Excludes Fuel)</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This is must do trip so book your slot now!&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#500050\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">To make a booking, click on the &quot;Official Ticket Site&quot; button.</span></span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-01-25', '2019-02-28', '19:00:00', '09:40:00', '1547742415.jpg', '1547745044.jpg', 18, '', 'http://www.holidaydada.in/contact-us.html', 'http://www.holidaydada.in/', 'https://www.facebook.com/holidaydada/', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 144, 0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-17 23:26:55', '2019-01-18 00:17:11'),
(89, 'F of X  2019- India\'s First Creative Forest Festival', 'f-of-x-creative-festival-2019', 4, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Is the creative fire inside of you not burning as brightly as it used to? If so, how would you like to attend.....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Embrace Creativity in the Heart of the Jungle- F of X Creative Forest festival</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Is the creative fire inside of you not burning as brightly as it used to? If so, how would you like to attend a 4-day festival that not only helps you grow your creative energy but takes place in the middle of the forest?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Take part in <strong>F of X Creative Forest Festival- a 4-day event</strong> that will be held in the forest of Jim Corbett National Park. <strong>Starting from the 21<sup>st</sup>&nbsp;of February&rsquo;19 and ending on the 24<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;of February, </strong>this experience will help you in amplifying &amp; improving your creative energy, finding yo&nbsp;creative voice and prosper in the company of fellow creative folks.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Professionals and attendees from different walks of life and different industries- Founders, Professionals, Rusty Creators, Corporate Misfits and explorers from Art, Music, Design, Fashion, Film, Food, Photography, Tech and genres that are yet to be defined- will all be there.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">What makes this event unique is that it&rsquo;s a very holistic experience, helping you not only enhance the creativity in your mind but also your heart, body and soul. Experience other creative forces, both in a conference setting or in the open at 2 am over a cup of hot coffee.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This is not an event, it&rsquo;s an experience. One that you cannot &amp; should not miss.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What do you get out of this event</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Incredible Group of People to </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">hangout</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> &amp; brainstorm with</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Learnings &amp; Insights from Creative Leaders</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Membership of an always growing collective. You will become part of the festival tribe, getting access to creators from different editions.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A Creative Intervention that will help you fine-tune your gameplan, to grow your creative journey.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Inclusions</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A 3Night, 4Day stay at a resort inside the forest. Separate rooms for girls &amp; guys, unless specifically requested otherwise.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Access to all sessions, workshops &amp; magic at </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fofx</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Comfortable buffets for breakfast, lunch and dinner on all the days.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Cost:</strong></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Come as a Trio - INR 23,000 PP</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Come as Duo - INR 25,000 PP</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Come </span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Solo</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> - INR 27,000 PP<br />\r\n	<span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All costs are per person. Costs are all inclusive of stay, food, experiences, activities, sessions &amp; workshops.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Limited seats left so book now! T</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#500050\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">o make a booking, click on the &quot;Official Ticket Site&quot; Button.</span></span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-02-21', '2019-02-24', '10:00:00', '20:05:00', '1547747684.jpg', '1547747684.jpg', 68, '', 'https://theexperienceco.typeform.com/to/Ftx4rx#homeheader', 'https://fofxfestival.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/FofXFestival/', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/fofx.festival/', '', '', '', 0, 215, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-18 00:54:44', '2019-01-18 01:04:35'),
(90, 'Benny Dayal and Funktuation live at Unmaad’19', 'benny-dayal-and-funktuation-live-at-unmaad19', 1, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Benny Dayal is best known for such popular songs like Pappu Can&#39;t Dance Sala, The Disco Song- Disco....</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ready for a night of </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">80s</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> and 90s funk?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Catch <strong>Benny Dayal and Funktuation live at Unmaad&rsquo;19</strong>- the cultural fest of <strong>IIM Bangalore on 2<sup>nd</sup>&nbsp;February 2019</strong>.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Benny Dayal is best known for such popular songs like Pappu Can&#39;t Dance Sala, The Disco Song- Disco Deewani &amp; Badtameez Dil. His contribution also extends to Malayalam, Telugu, Tamil and Bengali music, among others.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Go on a musical journey that Benny and Funktuation will take you on. Groove to the popular songs of that era and listen to the funky twists that they give to your favourites. And if that wasn&rsquo;t enough, Funktuation will also be bringing Electro Funk and Alt Rock music to the event. Hurrah!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Things to Remember: -</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Do not carry objectionable material (sharp objects, inflammable items, alcohol, bottles etc.).</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Due to limited space, parking will be offered on first come first serve basis.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Digital cameras, video cameras, etc. are NOT allowed.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can use your mobile phone.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-left: 36pt; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No Outside Food Allowed (Food stalls will be available at the venue)</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Early Bird prices are now live so get your tickets now!&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#500050\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">To make a booking, click on the &quot;Official Ticket Site&quot;&nbsp;button.</span></span></span></span></span></p>', '2019-02-02', '2019-02-02', '19:00:00', '22:30:00', '1547788946.jpg', '1547788946.jpg', 69, '', 'https://insider.in/event/benny-dayal-and-funktuation-live-at-launchpad-in-unmaad-19-feb2-2019/buy/shows/5c1c6cc90d845b0007b95f22?utm_source=Festeve-mantra&utm_medium=sports-category&utm_campa', 'http://www.unmaad.com/#home', 'https://www.facebook.com/unmaad.iimb/', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 168, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-18 12:22:26', '2019-01-18 12:22:26');
