(91, 'Learn UI & UX From Scratch - DesignBoat School', 'ui-and-ux-design-classroom-training-bangalore', 7, 0, '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This workshop will cover everything about UI &amp; UX, from basics to advanced ideas and programmes...</span></span></span></span></p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">UI &amp; UX have become critical components of product development &amp; deployment. For those unaware, UX refers to user experience while UI stands for </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">user</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> interface.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Both of them, together make up for a product&rsquo;s functionality. UI is the way in which a product is used while UX is a user&rsquo;s experience of using the product. For example, if you develop a mobile application then the different app screens are the UI, while the user&rsquo;s feedback would be UX. There are more layers to these principles, but the basics of each lie on what&rsquo;s written above.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">So, are you interested to learn about UI &amp; UX but confused where to start?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Worry not &amp; register for a hands-on <strong>14 weekends UI &amp; UX design classroom training programme</strong>. The programme commences from the <strong>28th of February 2019</strong>.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Organized by trained professionals, this workshop will cover everything about UI &amp; UX, from basics to advanced ideas and programmes. Through this course, you&rsquo;ll get a good grasp on UI &amp; UX, and will be propelled towards the right direction to pursue these as a career. Everything from design principles to understanding key designing solutions will be covered during this course.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The best part: the course is purely design-centric and requires 0 coding knowledge, so those without tech knowledge can participate without worry.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The classroom training will be conducted by some of the best professionals working in UI &amp; UX, across different industries. So rest assured that you will learn from the best, to be the best.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Who can attend this workshop?</strong></span></span></span></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People of any background.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People who would like to explore the field of UI/UX Design</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People from a Graphic Designing background</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">What </span></span></span></strong></u></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>you learn</strong></u></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">?</span></span></span></strong></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Adding the real-time emotion to the design is what a lot of designers lack. We believe in making our students driven and ready to build human-centric designs with the up-to-date idealistic approach. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">UX Designing&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">UI Designing</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Tools Used</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Portfolio &amp; Job</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Designboat</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"> UI/UX School helps you to make an ideal candidate with an eye for clean and artful design, possess superior UI skills and be able to translate high-level requirements into interaction flows and artifacts and transform them into beautiful, intuitive and functional user interfaces.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Click on the &quot;Official Ticket Site&quot; button to book your seat</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>', '2019-02-23', '2019-02-23', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', '1547836556.jpg', '1547836556.jpg', 70, '', 'http://www.designboatschool.in/contact-us', 'http://www.designboatschool.in/', 'https://www.facebook.com/www.designboat.in/', 'https://twitter.com/Design_Boat', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/designboat-ui-ux-studio/', 'https://www.instagram.com/designboatschool/?hl=en', '', '', '', 0, 56, 1, 1, 2, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-19 00:54:35', '2019-01-19 01:44:18'),
(92, 'Concert + Photo Exhibition: Make Like a Tree', 'live-concert-with-photo-exhibition-harkat-mumbai', 1, 0, '<p>Make Like a Tree is a photography exhibition &amp; concert conceptualized by Sergey Onischenko. Sergey....</p>', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">A Night for the Non-Conformists- Make Like a Tree Concert &amp; Photo Exhibition</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bored of the same old performances and concerts with electronic music blaring? There&rsquo;s something brewing that would be of interest to you.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Make Like a Tree</strong> is a photography exhibition &amp; concert conceptualized by <strong>Sergey Onischenko.</strong> Sergey is a Ukrainian who&rsquo;s hitch-hiking around the world, capturing minimalistic landscapes on his camera during his travels. His music is made up of non-conformist indie-folk tunes and Beat Generation ideas. The concerts he does are all performed in different parts of the world, with different members in each performance.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Unlike conventional musicians and concerts, be prepared to participate in the concert. Sergey involves the audience in his musical process, creating an active performance and a concert that involves everyone. The performance at Make Like a Tree will usher you into the inner circle of nature, comprising of woods, mountains and whale songs heard on the bottom of the ocean. This is a combination of music, photography &amp; video art, which have been curated during his years on the road.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The event will be held at Harkat Studios, Versova, Mumbai on February 3 and it starts at 7:30 PM.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This is not a concert, this is an experience. One that you&rsquo;ll cherish for as long as you live.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">To make a booking, click on the<strong> &quot;Official&nbsp;Ticket Site&quot;</strong>&nbsp;button.&nbsp;</span></p>', '2019-02-03', '2019-02-03', '19:30:00', '22:30:00', '1548002027.jpg', '1548002027.jpg', 71, '', 'https://insider.in/event/concert-photo-exhibition-make-like-a-tree-live-at-harkat-feb3-2019/buy/shows/5c175a3b7e76690007e0eb8b/Tickets?utm_source=Festeve-mantra&utm_medium=music-category&utm_', 'http://makelikeatreeband.tumblr.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/makelikeatreeband/', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/makelikeatree_official/?hl=en', '', '', '', 0, 120, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-20 23:33:47', '2019-01-21 02:18:35'),
(93, 'Aristocrat Marathon 2019 - The Battle Against HIV', 'aristocrat-marathon-march-2019-chennai', 2, 0, '<p>The 2019 Aristocrat Marathon is an effort to create awareness about HIV among children. The marathon...</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Run To Fight The Battle Against HIV- Aristocrat Marathon 2019 at Chennai</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Children are our greatest assets, but a lot of childhood dreams are lost towards the monstrosity that&rsquo;s HIV. This March take a stand and let&rsquo;s vow to fight HIV.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The <strong>2019 Aristocrat Marathon</strong> is an effort to create awareness about HIV among children. The marathon will be held on 10th March and will flag off from Olcott Memorial School, Besant Nagar, Chennai.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Why Should You Participate</strong></u></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Aristocrat Marathon is being held with one firm goal- Creating a brighter future for the HIV infected children&rsquo;s life and education. HIV stigma remains an unwanted reality and the high cost of medications, despite the support from the government, prevents many children from seeking medical assistance. Such kids also face discrimination from not only schools during admissions but are often abandoned by their families and left to fend for themselves.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">With your participation, we can all create a positive environment and create awareness about this social injustice. Not to mention, the funds generated will go in improving the lives of such kids, through medication, education &amp; basic needs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>The marathon will have 5 categories- 42KM, 21KM, 10KM, 5KM </strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>and</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong> 2KM runs, so participate in one you&rsquo;re most comfortable with.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Key Information</strong></u></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>3:00 am &ndash; Assembling time (Registration and bag check opens)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Start Time 42KM &ndash; &nbsp;3:30 am - Rs.950/-&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Start Time 21KM &ndash; &nbsp;4:30 am - Rs.900/-</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Start Time 10KM &ndash; &nbsp;5:30 am - Rs.850/-</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Start Time 5KM &ndash; 6:30 am - Rs.800/-</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Start Time 2KM &ndash; 7:00 am - Rs.750/-</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><u><strong>Inclusions</strong></u></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Marathon T-shirt</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bibs</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Participation Certificates</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Medals</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cash Prizes / Rewards for winners!</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Pre-event, Event and Post-event entertainment</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">This March join hands in the fight against HIV. To make a booking, click on the &quot;<strong>Official Ticket Site</strong>&quot; &nbsp;URL button.</span></span></p>', '2019-03-10', '2019-03-10', '03:30:00', '09:30:00', '1548005422.jpg', '1548005422.jpg', 72, '', 'https://www.meraevents.com/event/aristocrat-marathon-march-2019?acode=aAcuPF', 'http://aristocratmarathon.com/index.html', 'https://www.facebook.com/MarathonAristocrat/', 'https://twitter.com/AristoMarathon', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/aristocrat-marathon/', '', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/115284317499258832627', 'https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmue_7SmBMcfxmnIpKqkNDA', '', 0, 158, 0, 1, 2, 1, 1, 1, 'A', 0, '2019-01-21 00:30:22', '2019-01-21 00:40:57'),
(94, 'Biotech Galore- BioAsia 2019 Convention, Hyderabad', 'bioasia-2019-convention-hyderabad', 6, 0, '<p>Come be a part of BioAsia 2019- A 3-day event that will see the biggest names in biotechnology come....</p>', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">What happens when the world&rsquo;s pioneers in biotech convene at the same spot?</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Disruption happens, that&rsquo;s what!</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Come be a part of <strong>BioAsia 2019</strong>- A 3-day event that will see the biggest names in biotechnology come together for healthy discussions on biotechnology, its growth and where </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">its</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"> headed. </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Organised</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"> from <strong>25th Feb - 27th Feb 2019 at Hyderabad International Convention Centre (HICC)</strong>- Hyderabad, the theme for this year is&nbsp;<strong>Life Sciences 4.0</strong>&nbsp;where global experts will share their thoughts on global trends. People from different industries- companies, </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">policy-makers</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">, health-tech companies, start-ups, hospitals, scientists, etc, will be attending and sharing their thoughts at the event.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">At BioAsia, you&rsquo;ll find digital health start-ups and technology companies who are developing innovative and low-cost products, services and solutions. You&rsquo;ll learn and gain insight </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">on</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> the challenges that the industry faces and the achievements that have been made in the last year.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><u><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><strong>Why Should You Attend BioAsia?</strong></span></span></span></span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">BioAsia 2019 has been structured to help visitors understand how technology trends will impact business relationships and how disruptions in technology will impact collaboration opportunities in the industry. </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">BioAsia&rsquo;s</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"> tech conferences will include discussions on research developments and will assist you in learning about technological capabilities to break resistors. Experts &amp; leaders such as <strong>Mrs. Kiran Mazumdar Shaw</strong> (Chairman &amp; Managing Director, Biocon Ltd., India), <strong>Dr. Shreeram Aradhye</strong> (Chief Medical Officer, Novartis Pharmaceuticals, Switzerland), <strong>Dr. Sanat Chattopadhyay</strong> (EVP &amp; President, Merck Manufacturing Division - &lrm;Merck &amp; Co. Inc.) &amp; <strong>Dr. Raj K. Puri</strong> (Division Director, Center for Biologics Evaluation and Research, US FDA), will be there as speakers and </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">honourees</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">. Such cross-functional expertise across different biotech verticals sharing a </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">dias</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"> is sure to </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">simulate</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> your interest and will certainly help you in gaining knowledge that you will value forever.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justif