(30, 'Jeevesh Awal', '1545109905.jpg', 'Founder & CTO - Techmaniacs Eduservices', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Having 7 years of experience in coding in various languages, Jeevesh has trained more than 7000+ students all over India. His field of expertise includes Web &amp; Application development. Jeevesh has been a guest speaker at National Cyber Security Conference, the Computer Society of India, IIT Mumbai Techfest, IIT BHU - Technex and has been technically recommended by IIT BHU for technical excellence.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2018-12-18 12:11:45', '2018-12-18 12:11:45'),
